# Image OCR + Table Extraction Skill
Extract text and tabular data from images, scanned documents, and PDFs using Tesseract OCR engine with OpenCV preprocessing. Supports multi-language OCR (100+ languages), table structure detection, confidence scoring, orientation correction, and exports to CSV, JSON, and structured formats.
